Name: Unfinished Battle
About the game: Unfinished Battle is a fast paced rts game. Your mission is destroying the other castle and protect your own at the same time. Kill enemies earn gold and deploy more units. Finish this battle at all cost! 20 Level campaign. Boss Levels. Different strategy for each level. Medieval to Metal music that will put you in the game mood. Extremely hard to finish.
